An Act to Authorize the Release of Military Records to the Office of
Chief Medical Examiner for the Purposes of Suicide Reporting and
Prevention
Submitted by the Department of Defense, Veterans and Emergency Management pursuant
to Joint Rule 204.
Reference to the Committee on Veterans and Legal Affairs suggested and ordered printed.
ROBERT B. HUNT
